* [Milad Shafiee-Ashtiani, Aghil Yousefi-Koma, Masoud Shariat-Panahi, Majid Khadiv, Push Recovery of a Humanoid Robot Based on Model Predictive Control and Capture Point, 2016 IEEE/RSJ International Conference on Robotics and Mechatronics (ICROM 2016)](https://arxiv.org/pdf/1612.08034.pdf)

